2010.01.272010 IEEE/RSJ International Conference on Intelligent Robots and Systems  IROS 2010       The 2010 IEEE/RSJ International Conference on Intelligent Robots and Systems (IROS2010), to be held on October 18-22, 2010 in   Taipei International Convention Center (TICC) at Taipei, Taiwan,during 2010 Taiwan International Robot Week. In conjunction with  IROS2010 Conference, there are 2010 Taipei International Robot Show and several International Robotics Competitions will be taken place at the same venue. The conference is soliciting papers from the academic, industrial and government communities to present their results and to exchange ideas.For paper submissions and more information, please visit the conference website at: http://www.iros2010.org.tw

